content.text: The `frpm` table has `Enrollment (Ages 5-17)` and the `schools` table has `NCESSchool`. Let me query for the top 3 schools by enrollment, joining with the NCES school ID.

input.command: sqlite3 "/Users/david/workspace/claimdb/test_dbs/california_schools.sqlite" "SELECT s.NCESSchool, f.[Enrollment (Ages 5-17)] FROM frpm f JOIN schools s ON f.CDSCode = s.CDSCode WHERE f.[Enrollment (Ages 5-17)] IS NOT NULL ORDER BY f.[Enrollment (Ages 5-17)] DESC LIMIT 10;"
input.description: Get top 10 schools by Enrollment (Ages 5-17) with NCES school IDs

This matches the claim exactly.
